{
  "Phrases": [
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "It's good that you came - I must speak with you...",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24716
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 0,
      "ResponsesCount": 2,
      "TriggerIndex": 1,
      "Index": 0
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "First, I'm not what I seem.  I was transformed into this lemure form as punishment! ",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24719
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 2,
      "ResponsesCount": 2,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "Index": 1
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "Thank you.  My name is Ormis Dohor.  I am an archimandrite from the Black Raven Monastery.  I was invited to the Severed Hand to be held as a guest while a Severed Hand envoy, led by one called Dolon Daemba, stayed at Black Raven.",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24725
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 4,
      "ResponsesCount": 1,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "Index": 2
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "Shortly after my arrival here, I saw first hand the atrocities that Isair and Madae were capable of, particularly the slaves.  I voiced my protest, but that seemed to only anger Isair and Madae.  Evidently they were hoping that since I was half-drow I would be sympathetic to their cause.",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24814
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 5,
      "ResponsesCount": 1,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "Index": 3
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "They were wrong.  I informed them that the Black Raven Monastery would never align with, or even stand idly by, a kingdom that practices slavery.   So, as punishment for my *insolence,* they transformed me into this hideous form that stands before you.",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24815
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 6,
      "ResponsesCount": 2,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "Index": 4
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "Yes.  There is an antidote - at least I have been led to believe there's an antidote.  A Xvimian cleric, one who is called the Tyrannar Brutai Mar, holds the antidote.  He is a cruel, vicious man.",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24820
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 8,
      "ResponsesCount": 3,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "Index": 5
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "Once per week he will come to my cell with the antidote in his hand.  He tells me that if I cooperate with Isair and Madae, he will give me the antidote, and I will return to my natural form.",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24902
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 11,
      "ResponsesCount": 1,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "Index": 6
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "Each time he asks me, I refuse.  And each time I refuse, he pours a little bit of the antidote onto the floor.  With each pouring that he performs, I get closer to remaining in this form for the rest of my life.",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24903
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 12,
      "ResponsesCount": 1,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "Index": 7
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "If you could find the antidote and give it to me, perhaps there is still enough to turn me back.  I would be in your debt.",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24905
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 13,
      "ResponsesCount": 1,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "Index": 8
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "By the gods, that's it!  Thank you!  It feels glorious to be in my own body once more.  And know this, my friend, that if you intend to attack Madae and Isair, my men and I will be there to aid you in battle.  This I swear!",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24906
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 14,
      "ResponsesCount": 1,
      "TriggerIndex": 0,
      "Index": 9
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "I know that he spends most of his time in the Cleric's Tower.  Unfortunately, I do not know his exact location there.  You will have to search for him.",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24908
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 15,
      "ResponsesCount": 1,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "Index": 10
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "Thank you.   But be wary while in the Cleric's Tower - the place is overflowing with unholy magics and powerful clerics that won't hesitate to slaughter you.",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24910
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 16,
      "ResponsesCount": 1,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "Index": 11
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "You have returned!  Do you have the antidote?",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24912
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 17,
      "ResponsesCount": 2,
      "TriggerIndex": 2,
      "Index": 12
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "You have returned!  What is it you need?",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24918
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 19,
      "ResponsesCount": 3,
      "TriggerIndex": 4,
      "Index": 13
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "My name is Ormis Dohor.  I am an archimandrite from the Black Raven Monastery.  I was invited to Severed Hand to be held as a guest while a Severed Hand envoy, led by one called Dolon Daemba, stayed at Black Raven.",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 27608
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 22,
      "ResponsesCount": 1,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "Index": 14
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "You have returned!  Do you have the antidote?",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24912
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 23,
      "ResponsesCount": 1,
      "TriggerIndex": 3,
      "Index": 15
    }
  ],
  "Responses": [
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "Indeed...",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 35582
      },
      "JournalIndex": 0,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "ActionIndex": -1,
      "NextScriptDialog": "67Ormis",
      "NextPhraseIndex": 1,
      "Index": 0,
      "Flags": "HasText"
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "Get back, demon, I'll run you through!",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24717
      },
      "JournalIndex": 24709,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "ActionIndex": 0,
      "NextScriptDialog": "",
      "NextPhraseIndex": 0,
      "Index": 1,
      "Flags": "HasText, HasAction, HasNextDialog, HasJournal"
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "Very well, I'll hear you out - for now.",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24721
      },
      "JournalIndex": 0,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "ActionIndex": -1,
      "NextScriptDialog": "67Ormis",
      "NextPhraseIndex": 2,
      "Index": 2,
      "Flags": "HasText"
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "Liar!  Demons always twist the truth!  Prepare to die!",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24723
      },
      "JournalIndex": 24709,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "ActionIndex": 1,
      "NextScriptDialog": "",
      "NextPhraseIndex": 0,
      "Index": 3,
      "Flags": "HasText, HasAction, HasNextDialog, HasJournal"
    },
