      "NextScriptDialog": "67Ormis",
      "NextPhraseIndex": 4,
      "Index": 5,
      "Flags": "None"
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "Is there no way to change you back?",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24816
      },
      "JournalIndex": 24710,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "ActionIndex": 2,
      "NextScriptDialog": "67Ormis",
      "NextPhraseIndex": 5,
      "Index": 6,
      "Flags": "HasText, HasAction, HasJournal"
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "That is a very sad story, Ormis, but you'll have to excuse me for a moment, there's something I must attend to.",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24817
      },
      "JournalIndex": 0,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "ActionIndex": -1,
      "NextScriptDialog": "",
      "NextPhraseIndex": 0,
      "Index": 7,
      "Flags": "HasText, HasNextDialog"
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "What makes him so cruel?",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24821
      },
      "JournalIndex": 0,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "ActionIndex": -1,
      "NextScriptDialog": "67Ormis",
      "NextPhraseIndex": 6,
      "Index": 8,
      "Flags": "HasText"
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "Where might I find this Tyrannar Brutai Mar?",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24822
      },
      "JournalIndex": 0,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "ActionIndex": -1,
      "NextScriptDialog": "67Ormis",
      "NextPhraseIndex": 10,
      "Index": 9,
      "Flags": "HasText"
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "You're in luck, Ormis!  I ran into this Tyrannar you spoke of and found a bottle of strange liquid.  Take a look at it - is it the antidote?",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24901
      },
      "JournalIndex": 24708,
      "TriggerIndex": 0,
      "ActionIndex": 3,
      "NextScriptDialog": "",
      "NextPhraseIndex": 0,
      "Index": 10,
      "Flags": "HasText, HasTrigger, HasAction, HasNextDialog, HasJournal"
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": null,
        "Flags": "NoMessageData",
        "Sound": null,
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 0
      },
      "JournalIndex": 0,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "ActionIndex": -1,
      "NextScriptDialog": "67Ormis",
      "NextPhraseIndex": 7,
      "Index": 11,
      "Flags": "None"
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "That's horrendous!  What can I do to help?",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24904
      },
      "JournalIndex": 0,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "ActionIndex": -1,
      "NextScriptDialog": "67Ormis",
      "NextPhraseIndex": 8,
      "Index": 12,
      "Flags": "HasText"
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "Where might I find this Tyrannar Brutai Mar?",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24822
      },
      "JournalIndex": 0,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "ActionIndex": -1,
      "NextScriptDialog": "67Ormis",
      "NextPhraseIndex": 10,
      "Index": 13,
      "Flags": "HasText"
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "Then I owe you thanks, Ormis.  Until a later time.",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24907
      },
      "JournalIndex": 0,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "ActionIndex": 4,
      "NextScriptDialog": "",
      "NextPhraseIndex": 0,
      "Index": 14,
      "Flags": "HasText, HasAction, HasNextDialog"
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "I shall return with the antidote, Ormis.",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24909
      },
      "JournalIndex": 0,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "ActionIndex": -1,
      "NextScriptDialog": "67Ormis",
      "NextPhraseIndex": 11,
      "Index": 15,
      "Flags": "HasText"
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "Thanks for the warning.  Farewell.",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24911
      },
      "JournalIndex": 0,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "ActionIndex": -1,
      "NextScriptDialog": "",
      "NextPhraseIndex": 0,
      "Index": 16,
      "Flags": "HasText, HasNextDialog"
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "Yes, here it is.  *Hand Ormis the Antidote*",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24916
      },
      "JournalIndex": 41332,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "ActionIndex": 5,
      "NextScriptDialog": "",
      "NextPhraseIndex": 0,
      "Index": 17,
      "Flags": "HasText, HasAction, HasNextDialog, HasJournal"
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "No, I shall return when I do.",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 24917
      },
      "JournalIndex": 0,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "ActionIndex": -1,
      "NextScriptDialog": "",
      "NextPhraseIndex": 0,
      "Index": 18,
      "Flags": "HasText, HasNextDialog"
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "Tell me again who you are?",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 25834
      },
      "JournalIndex": 0,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "ActionIndex": -1,
      "NextScriptDialog": "67Ormis",
      "NextPhraseIndex": 14,
      "Index": 19,
      "Flags": "HasText"
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "Nothing. Never mind.",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 25835
      },
      "JournalIndex": 0,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "ActionIndex": -1,
      "NextScriptDialog": "",
      "NextPhraseIndex": 0,
      "Index": 20,
      "Flags": "HasText, HasNextDialog"
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "I've decided that you're lying and you must die.",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 27607
      },
      "JournalIndex": 0,
